com.leantegra.wibeat.sdk.monitoring.listeners

Interface BackgroundScanServiceConsumer

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ScanServiceConsumer
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AdvertisingNotificationManager

    public interface BackgroundScanServiceConsumer
extends ScanServiceConsumer
    The interface is used in BackgroundScanManager and provides callbacks indicating whether the service connection state has changed.

    Note: Ranging and monitoring of WiBeats is available after ScanServiceConsumer.onBind() callback.
    Since:
    1.4.0
    See Also:
    ScanServiceManager
